 Day1Part2←{
     ⍺←50 0
     0=⍴⍵:⍺
     (cur tail)←(⊃⍵)(1↓⍵)

     ⍝ The raw impact of the current turn
     raw←(⍎1↓cur)×¯1+2×⊃cur='R'
     ⍝ The number of full rotations in the current turn
     r←⌊(|raw)÷100
     ⍝ The net impact of the current turn
     net←raw-(×raw)×r×100
     ⍝ The actual new position
     n←100|(⊃⍺+net)
     n(⍺[2]+0=n)∇ tail
 }
